Text-to-Speech Web Application

This is a simple text-to-speech web application that allows users to enter text in a textarea and convert it to speech using the Web Speech API.

Features
Input text into a textarea.
Click a button to hear the text spoken aloud.
Uses the Web Speech API for text-to-speech functionality.
Simple and clean user interface.


Files
index.html: The main HTML file that contains the structure of the webpage.
styles.css: The CSS file that styles the webpage.
script.js: The JavaScript file that handles the text-to-speech functionality.

